what i’ve learned is that for PRs that trigger all the tests (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/58134, https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/58282), it’s literally impossible for Cypress to pass :sob:  so many 502s and timeouts…

hopefully things will get better with a dedicated AI Hub environment for Cypress tests! :pray:
